long_description: since our dance program's inception in 2010, we have been embraced by the local community, experiencing tremendous growth and spreading positivity. break city holds the distinction of being canada's first and only dance school specializing in breakin'. we take great pride in empowering today's youth through the rich elements of hip hop. our goal is to provide a nurturing environment where students can explore their artistic potential, express themselves freely, and develop life skills that go beyond the dance floor. our classes go beyond the ordinary, focusing on character-building and personal growth. each choreography revolves around a unique creative theme, encouraging students to unleash their imagination and connect with the music on a deeper level. join us at break city, and let us guide you on a remarkable journey of self-discovery and artistic fulfillment. meet chris and tiff, the passionate owners of break city. chris, a seasoned bboy, and tiff, a versatile dancer, are dedicated to creating a supportive and inclusive community.
